A United Kingdom-based actress, singer and entrepreneur, Ajoke Peters, aka Ajay Peters, says though she is involved in a quite a number of activities, she always puts her best into whatever she does. Peters, who also hosts a podcast named, ‘What’s Good with Ajay’, maintained that she has her eyes set on making a name for herself in the entertainment industry. She told Sunday Scoop, “To say I am passionate about whatever I do is an understatement. I give my best to everything I do, whether it is my podcast, music or movies. I can assure entertainment lovers out there that they are about to see more of me. My mantra is, ‘Whatever I do, I do it right’. I am versatile and don’t want to be put in a box. “Aside from my skincare business, I have recorded songs with some top Nigerian artistes. I have even appeared in the music videos of some of them.” Shedding more light on her podcast, she said, “It has helped several young ladies and women to bare their minds on issues that affect them, and we have been able to get solutions for some of them.”  Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com